{"tid":1456533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場多人 機場多人 機場多人","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:56:40.000Z","uid":49246,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca492115c2e25dee13389bc2a6602a220f73bac","tid":1456533,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"唔係盲目戀戰<br />\n只不過唔好咁易比所謂既消息打沉 一聽到就走<br />\n冇錯我地做其中一個目的 令所有航班取消<br />\n但唔可以比大陸佬咁撚易打散我地 傳幾個訊息<br />\n較暗張相就話熄燈<br />\n<br />\n大家冷靜啲 現場見到唔少手足係度互屌人散水狗<br />\n大陸林鄭就係想見到我地咁樣<br />\n再係咁咪正中佢地下懷"},{"pid":"b39b0df8542b38d362a41c600d0f38cbfcb74cb8","tid":1456533,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a025e9c74d22a032127cd5ca06bbaa003b856419","tid":1456533,"uid":49246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"不分化<br />\n唔好自己人屌自己人<br />\n互相尊重<br />\n<br />\n唔好中大陸林鄭下懷"},{"pid":"a9f2e992125b99dd93c1b8b5531787fc2ceeffaf","tid":1456533,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"891eb44323648096dff3b57953386db7030474b5","tid":1456533,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀快啲！"},{"pid":"41a76239f68e547b2a9c226c5fc8cbe8c8083a57","tid":1456533,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"快撚啲呀"},{"pid":"7a6e8ccaba85728b655e81d25b8e50f616a40838","tid":1456533,"uid":69719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"956572258679ddcd26c895cbca5c9f6ac180b0b2","tid":1456533,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"屌推呀"},{"pid":"67b613d1b426306e4c6812297d4e8585764283cf","tid":1456533,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"57c7891a7713db511c8